{"tid":1587613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要解放新屋嶺！","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:51:36.000Z","uid":70422,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae3cc267899b436a03091460d7bd821a13e0234","tid":1587613,"uid":70422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190922/mobile/bkn-20190922194044400-0922_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190922%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190922194044400-0922_00822_001.html&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=47ba57cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190922/mobile/bkn-20190922194044400-0922_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日(22日)晚上6時許，文錦渡路新屋嶺發生山火，出現2條分別約10米及5米長火龍，消防接報派員到場，帶同滅火拍、背泵等工具登山撲救。其後，消防將山火救熄，毋須疏散。新屋嶺有一個扣留中心，部分近日在示威衝突中被捕的人士，正在上址扣查。"},{"pid":"d5746fdbc2d15c0bab41a06350e210de6cdd6a57","tid":1587613,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"153a6d2963540952e7ec82d6a7a6b7236375deba","tid":1587613,"uid":234089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"真心 個到一定要人多 要好多勇武 最小幾萬<br />\n唔係既話 難聽講句 真心送頭"},{"pid":"876d8f7b7b5a703fbe39d8838567b767c9e1286d","tid":1587613,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"「927 聲援及關注新屋嶺被捕者人權集會」<br />\n日期：2019年9月27日(星期五)<br />\n時間：晚上8時正開始<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n（不反對通知書申請中，存在變數）<br />\n（請加入頻道以便接收最新消息）<br />\n<br />\nTG CHANNEL: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/VictimConcern\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FVictimConcern&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=8895d7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_